            <!-- Divider -->
            <hr class="hr-md mb-7 mx-auto" />

            <!-- Text -->
            <p class="mb-0">
              Jazztel was still in need of capital to fund its growth profile generated from a high level of investment at a maximum execution speed. But the capital structure was left without any more room and reached a point where even and especially banks were not supportive.
              Banks took part of the IPO, of the HY papers raised, even with a convertible bond and there is the instrument we decided to use. Purpose was to help Jazztel transitionning from a overhang debt structure to a most balanced equity/debt structure to reflect its full potential.
            </p>
